{"tid":1283504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉曉明批英國站錯邊支持暴力犯罪　英方指言論不能接受","createTime":"2019-07-03T23:05:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T00:16:01.000Z","uid":53003,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2fdd180c47e1e51c1a8bb1feea425f948b568b8e","tid":1283504,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T23:05:25.000Z","msg":"中國駐英大使劉曉明說，日前不合法佔據香港立法會大樓的人，應被視為犯罪份子予以譴責，英國支持暴力犯罪者是「站錯邊」，警告英方避免進一步干預，否則有可能進一步損害雙邊關係。<br />\n<br />\n英國外交部傳召劉曉明，指出他的言論「不準確及不能接受」。首相文翠珊較早前說，香港的高度自治，及《中英聯合聲明》中訂明的權利與自由得到尊重，至關重要。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466532-20190704.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466532-20190704.htm&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O9%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=feb913a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466532-20190704.htm&h=3f3ed9a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466532-20190704.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2bb4850d76bb721b5c8434cbbab70ed18dd6c800","tid":1283504,"uid":103230,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T23:11:26.000Z","msg":"英國心諗已經盡力同你兜緊一國兩際運作順利<br />\n<br />\n你屌鳩我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a0382c338db0bf870b5ca3bb9b91005ec3daff","tid":1283504,"uid":1241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2bb4850d76bb721b5c8434cbbab70ed18dd6c800","tid":1283504,"uid":103230,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T23:11:26.000Z","msg":"英國心諗已經盡力同你兜緊一國兩際運作順利<br />\n<br />\n你屌鳩我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T23:15:12.000Z","msg":"下次扯爛佢塊假面具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\